My, to meet again in a place like
this is quite the coincidence, mo!

rows.label: tlk000601_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The inn I always patronize
is called Jakolo's, mo.

rows.label: tlk000601_01_msg0003
rows.name:
It's in the Beraf Industrial Ward,
and the hot springs are so pleasant,
it's a wonderful place, mo~!

rows.label: tlk000601_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I'll tell them to give you
a cheap room, so please be
sure to stop by, mo.
